This function returns all available publications from an operation or a date

Usage

get_publications(
  code = NULL,
  resource = "all",
  help = FALSE,
  det = 0,
  ioe = FALSE,
  lang = "ES"
)

Arguments

code

(string) operation or publication indentificator

resource

(string) resource to access, by default resource = "all" to get serie metadata. Possible values are all, operation or date

help

(boolean) type any value for resource param and type help = TRUE to see params available for this resource.

det

(int) det = 2 to see two levels of depth, specifically to access the PubFechaAct object, det = 0 by default

ioe

(boolean) TRUE if code is in format IO30138, and FALSE by default

lang

(string) language used to obtain information
